Titolo: Neverwinter Nights: Hordes of the Underdark

Anno: 2003

Descrizione: Neverwinter Nights: Hordes of the Underdark is an expansion pack for the role-playing video game Neverwinter Nights produced by BioWare and published by Atari. The follow-up to the Shadows of Undrentide expansion, Hordes of the Underdark adds a campaign, prestige classes, and other features. The Windows version also includes new scripting options for the Aurora toolkit.

Genere: Role-playing 

Valutazione: N/A
